                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontsize='12'>Company_22’s workforce is predominantly low-to-moderate risk, with a meaningful portion requiring dependent coverage. While most employees are unlikely to drive high costs, a smaller segment with chronic conditions represents concentrated long-term risk exposure.</run>
